{"tid":660022,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"53歲利迷生命垂危！歐聯4強前被羅馬球迷襲擊","createTime":"2018-05-10T10:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T16:50:42.000Z","uid":20634,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4b25f0a735ffef34a96ae4bcac1ed4d1d34e32b0","tid":660022,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"　　BBC消息，被羅馬球迷襲擊的利物浦球迷肖恩-西蒙確斯依然生命垂危。<br />\n<br />\n　　在上個月利物浦主場對羅馬的歐聯4強比賽前，53歲的西蒙確斯頭部遭到羅馬球迷的錘子襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n　　之後西蒙確斯一直處於昏迷狀態，家人表示他是一名鬥士，但他的情況依然非常嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n　　西蒙確斯的家人表示，全世界的支持在最黑暗的時刻鼓舞了他們。西蒙確斯來自愛爾蘭，球迷自發為他籌款，利物浦球員和球會都送上了支持。<br />\n<br />\n　　兩名涉案的意大利男子已經被逮捕並遭到起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/05/10/1/16ecb0a7912da1bf8c7ce8a248f8b2b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F1%2F16ecb0a7912da1bf8c7ce8a248f8b2b4.jpg&h=11e4a369&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d28153d8d60790eaaf86b4b3727b0e52c3afa74","tid":660022,"uid":1984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"8a90a914c88a73d785b1d4fe6ef18c787cc1583a","tid":660022,"uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"羅馬狗痴撚線"},{"pid":"d7f8fc642d5ebd42f8b42b2033a6faca521622c0","tid":660022,"uid":14872,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:01:49.000Z","msg":"意大利=歐洲支那"},{"pid":"88889d968d1a0443d4861d4fd8c49803948ce422","tid":660022,"uid":23878,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"點會係羅馬迷，所有對利物蒲不利都應該係曼迷先岩。<br />\nBtw 快啲好返睇利奪冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe823d1e17327294438c856a85cf5e330e1ee0f2","tid":660022,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"53歲（昏迷）"},{"pid":"78d86a0ef5fb5b0b09cec0f8473072d1de41bd85","tid":660022,"uid":153120,"like":29,"dislike":4,"scor